description.narrative:
Activities include:

1) Developing a coalition steering committee; 

2) Developing a broad-based coalition with multi-sector support; 

3) Raising awareness on second hand smoke dangers; 

4) Recruiting 10 multi-unit buildings across the four key neighborhoods to target for smoke-free policy adoption; 

5) Determining support for smoke-free building policies in targeted buildings; 

6) Promoting the benefits of smoke-free policies; 

7) Adapting smoke-free building policies and implementation procedures; 

8) Planning for Minneapolis city smoke-free ordinance in multi-unit buildings; 

9) Advocating for Minneapolis multi-unit housing smoke-free ordinance.
